Ellen White Means to Me, </div><div class="t m709 x62 h24 y512 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as well as numerous </div><div class="t meb8 xc5 h24 yaaf ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">articles in Adventist periodicals. </div><div class="t m309 x49 h24 y12a9 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dr. Douglass enjoys studying contemporary theological trends, </div><div class="t m8a8 xc5 h24 y138 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gardening, and landscaping. He is married and has four adult </div><div class="t m75b xc5 h24 yeb ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">children. </div><div class="t mda9 x63 h6b y1196 ff4 fs27 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Check with your local Adventist Book </div><div class="t m220 x63 h6b y1126 ff4 fs27 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Center for the companion book to the </div><div class="t macf x63 h6b y1394 ff4 fs27 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath School lessons. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
